// Hand-maintained: NOT generated by mmtorust.
//
// Rust port of `OMCompiler/Compiler/Util/TaskGraphResults.mo`, whose bodies
// are all `external "C"` wrappers over
// `OMCompiler/Compiler/runtime/TaskGraphResultsCmp.cpp`. mmtorust can only
// emit `todo!()` for `external "C"` bodies, so this module is hand-written
// and `TaskGraphResults` is listed in `HANDWRITTEN_TOP_PACKAGES`
// (mmtorust/src/codegen.rs) to skip its codegen.
//
// The hpcom testsuite checks the task graph the backend dumped (GraphML via
// `GraphML.mo`) against a reference GraphML file (`checkTaskGraph`) or
// against `// TG_NODE:`/`// TG_DEPENDENCY:` comments in generated code
// (`checkCodeGraph`). The comparison is structural: same node multiset (by
// name resp. id), same edge multiset (by source/target), every node carrying
// a calculation time and every edge a communication time (GraphML vs GraphML
// only). All diagnostic strings are kept byte-identical to the C++ since
// they appear in expected test output.

